{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"My story actually began when I was four years old"},{"time":3000,"text":"and my family moved to a new neighborhood"},{"time":5000,"text":"in our hometown of Savannah, Georgia."},{"time":7000,"text":"And this was the 1960s"},{"time":9000,"text":"when actually all the streets in this neighborhood"},{"time":11000,"text":"were named after Confederate war generals."},{"time":14000,"text":"We lived on Robert E. Lee Boulevard."},{"time":16000,"text":"And when I was five,"},{"time":18000,"text":"my parents gave me an orange Schwinn Sting-Ray bicycle."},{"time":21000,"text":"It had a swooping banana seat and those ape hanger handlebars"},{"time":24000,"text":"that made the rider look like an orangutan."},{"time":27000,"text":"That's why they were called ape hangers."},{"time":29000,"text":"They were actually modeled on hotrod motorcycles of the 1960s,"},{"time":32000,"text":"which I'm sure my mom didn't know."},{"time":34000,"text":"And one day I was exploring this cul-de-sac"},{"time":37000,"text":"hidden away a few streets away."},{"time":39000,"text":"And I came back,"},{"time":41000,"text":"and I wanted to turn around and get back to that street more quickly,"},{"time":43000,"text":"so I decided to turn around in this big street"},{"time":46000,"text":"that intersected our neighborhood,"},{"time":48000,"text":"and wham! I was hit by a passing sedan."},{"time":51000,"text":"My mangled body flew in one direction,"},{"time":53000,"text":"my mangled bike flew in the other."},{"time":56000,"text":"And I lay on the pavement stretching over that yellow line,"},{"time":59000,"text":"and one of my neighbors came running over."},{"time":61000,"text":"\"Andy, Andy, how are you doing?\" she said, using the name of my older brother."},{"time":64000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":66000,"text":"\"I'm Bruce,\" I said, and promptly passed out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"I broke my left femur that day --"},{"time":71000,"text":"it's the largest bone in your body --"},{"time":73000,"text":"and spent the next two months in a body cast"},{"time":76000,"text":"that went from my chin to the tip of my toe"},{"time":78000,"text":"to my right knee,"},{"time":80000,"text":"and a steel bar went from my right knee"},{"time":82000,"text":"to my left ankle."},{"time":84000,"text":"And for the next 38 years,"},{"time":86000,"text":"that accident was the only medically interesting thing"},{"time":88000,"text":"that ever happened to me."},{"time":91000,"text":"In fact, I made a living by walking."},{"time":93000,"text":"I traveled around the world, entered different cultures,"},{"time":95000,"text":"wrote a series of books about my travels,"},{"time":97000,"text":"including \"Walking the Bible.\""},{"time":99000,"text":"I hosted a television show by that name"},{"time":101000,"text":"on PBS."},{"time":103000,"text":"I was, for all the world, the \"walking guy.\""},{"time":106000,"text":"Until, in May 2008,"},{"time":109000,"text":"a routine visit to my doctor"},{"time":111000,"text":"and a routine blood test"},{"time":113000,"text":"produced evidence in the form of an alkaline phosphatase number"},{"time":116000,"text":"that something might be wrong with my bones."},{"time":120000,"text":"And my doctor, on a whim, sent me to get a full-body bone scan,"},{"time":123000,"text":"which showed that there was some growth in my left leg."},{"time":126000,"text":"That sent me to an X-ray, then to an MRI."},{"time":129000,"text":"And one afternoon, I got a call from my doctor."},{"time":133000,"text":"\"The tumor in your leg"},{"time":135000,"text":"is not consistent with a benign tumor.\""},{"time":137000,"text":"I stopped walking,"},{"time":139000,"text":"and it took my mind a second to convert that double negative"},{"time":142000,"text":"into a much more horrifying negative."},{"time":144000,"text":"I have cancer."},{"time":146000,"text":"And to think that the tumor was in the same bone,"},{"time":149000,"text":"in the same place in my body"},{"time":151000,"text":"as the accident 38 years earlier --"},{"time":154000,"text":"it seemed like too much of a coincidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"So that afternoon, I went back to my house,"},{"time":159000,"text":"and my three year-old identical twin daughters, Eden and Tybee Feiler,"},{"time":162000,"text":"came running to meet me."},{"time":164000,"text":"They'd just turned three,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and they were into all things pink and purple."},{"time":168000,"text":"In fact, we called them Pinkalicious and Purplicious --"},{"time":171000,"text":"although I must say, our favorite nickname"},{"time":173000,"text":"occurred on their birthday, April 15th."},{"time":175000,"text":"When they were born at 6:14 and 6:46"},{"time":178000,"text":"on April 15, 2005,"},{"time":181000,"text":"our otherwise grim, humorless doctor looked at his watch,"},{"time":183000,"text":"and was like, \"Hmm, April 15th -- tax day."},{"time":186000,"text":"Early filer and late filer.\""},{"time":189000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":194000,"text":"The next day I came to see him. I was like, \"Doctor, that was a really good joke.\""},{"time":197000,"text":"And he was like, \"You're the writer, kid.\""},{"time":199000,"text":"Anyway -- so they had just turned three,"},{"time":201000,"text":"and they came and they were doing this dance they had just made up"},{"time":203000,"text":"where they were twirling faster and faster until they tumbled to the ground,"},{"time":206000,"text":"laughing with all the glee in the world."},{"time":209000,"text":"I crumbled."},{"time":211000,"text":"I kept imagining all the walks I might not take with them,"},{"time":214000,"text":"the art projects I might not mess up,"},{"time":216000,"text":"the boyfriends I might not scowl at,"},{"time":218000,"text":"the aisles I might not walk down."},{"time":221000,"text":"Would they wonder who I was, I thought."},{"time":223000,"text":"Would they yearn for my approval,"},{"time":225000,"text":"my love, my voice?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"A few days later, I woke with an idea"},{"time":230000,"text":"of how I might give them that voice."},{"time":232000,"text":"I would reach out to six men"},{"time":234000,"text":"from all parts of my life"},{"time":236000,"text":"and ask them to be present"},{"time":238000,"text":"in the passages of my daughters' lives."},{"time":241000,"text":"\"I believe my girls will have plenty of opportunities in their lives,\""},{"time":243000,"text":"I wrote these men."},{"time":245000,"text":"\"They'll have loving families and welcoming homes,"},{"time":247000,"text":"but they may not have me."},{"time":249000,"text":"They may not have their dad."},{"time":251000,"text":"Will you help be their dad?\""},{"time":253000,"text":"And I said to myself"},{"time":255000,"text":"I would call this group of men \"the Council of Dads.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":259000,"text":"Now as soon as I had this idea,"},{"time":261000,"text":"I decided I wouldn't tell my wife. Okay."},{"time":264000,"text":"She's a very upbeat,"},{"time":266000,"text":"naturally excited person."},{"time":268000,"text":"There's this idea in this culture -- I don't have to tell you --"},{"time":271000,"text":"that you sort of \"happy\" your way through a problem."},{"time":273000,"text":"We should focus on the positive."},{"time":275000,"text":"My wife, as I said, she grew up outside of Boston."},{"time":277000,"text":"She's got a big smile. She's got a big personality."},{"time":279000,"text":"She's got big hair --"},{"time":281000,"text":"although, she told me recently, I can't say she has big hair,"},{"time":284000,"text":"because if I say she has big hair,"},{"time":286000,"text":"people will think she's from Texas."},{"time":288000,"text":"And it's apparently okay to marry a boy from Georgia,"},{"time":290000,"text":"but not to have hair from Texas."},{"time":293000,"text":"And actually, in her defense, if she were here right now,"},{"time":295000,"text":"she would point out that, when we got married in Georgia,"},{"time":298000,"text":"there were three questions"},{"time":300000,"text":"on the marriage certificate license,"},{"time":302000,"text":"the third of which was, \"Are you related?\""},{"time":305000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":308000,"text":"I said, \"Look, in Georgia at least we want to know."},{"time":310000,"text":"In Arkansas they don't even ask.\""},{"time":313000,"text":"What I didn't tell her is, if she said, \"Yes,\" you could jump."},{"time":315000,"text":"You don't need the 30-day waiting period."},{"time":317000,"text":"Because you don't need the get-to-know-you session at that point."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"So I wasn't going to tell her about this idea,"},{"time":322000,"text":"but the next day I couldn't control myself, I told her."},{"time":324000,"text":"And she loved the idea,"},{"time":326000,"text":"but she quickly started rejecting my nominees."},{"time":330000,"text":"She was like, \"Well, I love him, but I would never ask him for advice.\""},{"time":333000,"text":"So it turned out that starting a council of dads"},{"time":335000,"text":"was a very efficient way to find out"},{"time":337000,"text":"what my wife really thought of my friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"So we decided that we needed a set of rules,"},{"time":343000,"text":"and we came up with a number."},{"time":345000,"text":"And the first one was no family, only friends."},{"time":347000,"text":"We thought our family would already be there."},{"time":349000,"text":"Second, men only."},{"time":351000,"text":"We were trying to fill the dad-space in the girls' lives."},{"time":353000,"text":"And then third, sort of a dad for every side."},{"time":356000,"text":"We kind of went through my personality"},{"time":358000,"text":"and tried to get a dad who represented each different thing."},{"time":360000,"text":"So what happened was I wrote a letter to each of these men."},{"time":362000,"text":"And rather than send it,"},{"time":364000,"text":"I decided to read it to them in person."},{"time":367000,"text":"Linda, my wife, joked that it was like having six different marriage proposals."},{"time":370000,"text":"I sort of friend-married each of these guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373000,"text":"And the first of these guys was Jeff Schumlin."},{"time":375000,"text":"Now Jeff led this trip I took to Europe"},{"time":377000,"text":"when I graduated from high school in the early 1980s."},{"time":380000,"text":"And on that first day we were in this youth hostel in a castle."},{"time":383000,"text":"And I snuck out behind,"},{"time":385000,"text":"and there was a moat, a fence and a field of cows."},{"time":388000,"text":"And Jeff came up beside me and said,"},{"time":390000,"text":"\"So, have you ever been cow tipping?\""},{"time":392000,"text":"I was like, \"Cow tipping?"},{"time":394000,"text":"He was like, \"Yeah. Cows sleep standing up."},{"time":396000,"text":"So if you approach them from behind, down wind,"},{"time":399000,"text":"you can push them over and they go thud in the mud.\""},{"time":401000,"text":"So before I had a chance to determine whether this was right or not,"},{"time":404000,"text":"we had jumped the moat, we had climbed the fence,"},{"time":406000,"text":"we were tiptoeing through the dung"},{"time":408000,"text":"and approaching some poor, dozing cow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412000,"text":"So a few weeks after my diagnosis,"},{"time":414000,"text":"we went up to Vermont,"},{"time":416000,"text":"and I decided to put Jeff as the first person in the Council of Dads."},{"time":419000,"text":"And we went to this apple orchard, and I read him this letter."},{"time":422000,"text":"\"Will you help be their dad?\""},{"time":424000,"text":"And I got to the end -- he was crying and I was crying --"},{"time":426000,"text":"and then he looked at me, and he said, \"Yes.\""},{"time":428000,"text":"I was like, \"Yes?\""},{"time":430000,"text":"I kind of had forgotten there was a question at the heart of my letter."},{"time":432000,"text":"And frankly, although I keep getting asked this,"},{"time":434000,"text":"it never occurred to me that anybody would turn me down"},{"time":436000,"text":"under the circumstances."},{"time":439000,"text":"And then I asked him a question, which I ended up asking to all the dads"},{"time":442000,"text":"and ended up really encouraging me to write this story down in a book."},{"time":445000,"text":"And that was, \"What's the one piece of advice"},{"time":447000,"text":"you would give to my girls?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":449000,"text":"And Jeff's advice was,"},{"time":451000,"text":"\"Be a traveller, not a tourist."},{"time":453000,"text":"Get off the bus. Seek out what's different."},{"time":456000,"text":"Approach the cow.\""},{"time":458000,"text":"\"So it's 10 years from now,\" I said,"},{"time":460000,"text":"\"and my daughters are about to take their first trip abroad, and I'm not here."},{"time":463000,"text":"What would you tell them?\""},{"time":465000,"text":"He said, \"I would approach this journey"},{"time":467000,"text":"as a young child might approach a mud puddle."},{"time":469000,"text":"You can bend over and look at your reflection in the mirror"},{"time":472000,"text":"and maybe run your finger and make a small ripple,"},{"time":475000,"text":"or you can jump in and thrash around"},{"time":477000,"text":"and see what it feels like, what it smells like.\""},{"time":480000,"text":"And as he talked he had that glint in his eye"},{"time":482000,"text":"that I first saw back in Holland --"},{"time":484000,"text":"the glint that says, \"Let's go cow tipping,\""},{"time":486000,"text":"even though we never did tip the cow,"},{"time":489000,"text":"even though no one tips the cow,"},{"time":491000,"text":"even though cows don't sleep standing up."},{"time":495000,"text":"He said, \"I want to see you back here girls, at the end of this experience,"},{"time":498000,"text":"covered in mud.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":503000,"text":"Two weeks after my diagnosis, a biopsy confirmed"},{"time":505000,"text":"I had a seven-inch osteosarcoma"},{"time":507000,"text":"in my left femur."},{"time":509000,"text":"Six hundred Americans a year get an osteosarcoma."},{"time":512000,"text":"Eighty-five percent are under 21."},{"time":514000,"text":"Only a hundred adults a year"},{"time":516000,"text":"get one of these diseases."},{"time":518000,"text":"Twenty years ago, doctors would have cut off my leg and hoped,"},{"time":521000,"text":"and there was a 15 percent survival rate."},{"time":524000,"text":"And then in the 1980's, they determined"},{"time":526000,"text":"that one particular cocktail of chemo could be effective,"},{"time":529000,"text":"and within weeks I had started that regimen."},{"time":532000,"text":"And since we are in a medical room,"},{"time":534000,"text":"I went through four and a half months of chemo."},{"time":536000,"text":"Actually I had Cisplatin, Doxorubicin"},{"time":538000,"text":"and very high-dose Methotrexate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541000,"text":"And then I had a 15-hour surgery"},{"time":543000,"text":"in which my surgeon, Dr. John Healey"},{"time":545000,"text":"at Memorial Sloan-Kettering Hospital in New York,"},{"time":547000,"text":"took out my left femur"},{"time":549000,"text":"and replaced it with titanium."},{"time":552000,"text":"And if you did see the Sanjay special,"},{"time":554000,"text":"you saw these enormous screws"},{"time":556000,"text":"that they screwed into my pelvis."},{"time":558000,"text":"Then he took my fibula from my calf,"},{"time":561000,"text":"cut it out and then relocated it to my thigh,"},{"time":564000,"text":"where it now lives."},{"time":566000,"text":"And what he actually did was he de-vascularized it from my calf"},{"time":569000,"text":"and re-vascularized it in my thigh"},{"time":571000,"text":"and then connected it"},{"time":573000,"text":"to the good parts of my knee and my hip."},{"time":576000,"text":"And then he took out a third of my quadriceps muscle."},{"time":579000,"text":"This is a surgery so rare"},{"time":581000,"text":"only two human beings have survived it before me."},{"time":584000,"text":"And my reward for surviving it"},{"time":586000,"text":"was to go back for four more months of chemo."},{"time":589000,"text":"It was, as we said in my house,"},{"time":591000,"text":"a lost year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593000,"text":"Because in those opening weeks, we all had nightmares."},{"time":596000,"text":"And one night I had a nightmare that I was walking through my house,"},{"time":598000,"text":"sat at my desk and saw photographs of someone else's children"},{"time":601000,"text":"sitting on my desk."},{"time":603000,"text":"And I remember a particular one night that, when you told that story of --"},{"time":606000,"text":"I don't know where you are Dr. Nuland --"},{"time":608000,"text":"of William Sloane Coffin --"},{"time":610000,"text":"it made me think of it."},{"time":612000,"text":"Because I was in the hospital after, I think it was my fourth round of chemo"},{"time":615000,"text":"when my numbers went to zero, and I had basically no immune system."},{"time":618000,"text":"And they put me in an infectious disease ward at the hospital."},{"time":621000,"text":"And anybody who came to see me had to cover themselves in a mask"},{"time":624000,"text":"and cover all of the extraneous parts of their body."},{"time":628000,"text":"And one night I got a call from my mother-in-law"},{"time":630000,"text":"that my daughters, at that time three and a half,"},{"time":632000,"text":"were missing me and feeling my absence."},{"time":635000,"text":"And I hung up the phone,"},{"time":637000,"text":"and I put my face in my hands,"},{"time":639000,"text":"and I screamed this silent scream."},{"time":643000,"text":"And what you said, Dr. Nuland -- I don't know where you are --"},{"time":645000,"text":"made me think of this today."},{"time":647000,"text":"Because the thought that came to my mind"},{"time":649000,"text":"was that the feeling that I had"},{"time":651000,"text":"was like a primal scream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653000,"text":"And what was so striking --"},{"time":655000,"text":"and one of the messages I want to leave you here with today --"},{"time":658000,"text":"is the experience."},{"time":660000,"text":"As I became less and less human --"},{"time":663000,"text":"and at this moment in my life, I was probably 30 pounds less than I am right now."},{"time":666000,"text":"Of course, I had no hair and no immune system."},{"time":669000,"text":"They were actually putting blood inside my body."},{"time":672000,"text":"At that moment I was less and less human,"},{"time":674000,"text":"I was also, at the same time,"},{"time":676000,"text":"maybe the most human I've ever been."},{"time":679000,"text":"And what was so striking about that time"},{"time":682000,"text":"was, instead of repulsing people,"},{"time":684000,"text":"I was actually proving to be a magnet for people."},{"time":686000,"text":"People were incredibly drawn."},{"time":688000,"text":"When my wife and I had kids, we thought it would be all-hands-on-deck."},{"time":691000,"text":"Instead, it was everybody running the other way."},{"time":693000,"text":"And when I had cancer, we thought it'd be everybody running the other way."},{"time":696000,"text":"Instead, it was all-hands-on-deck."},{"time":698000,"text":"And when people came to me,"},{"time":700000,"text":"rather than being incredibly turned off by what they saw --"},{"time":702000,"text":"I was like a living ghost --"},{"time":704000,"text":"they were incredibly moved"},{"time":706000,"text":"to talk about what was going on in their own lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709000,"text":"Cancer, I found, is a passport to intimacy."},{"time":712000,"text":"It is an invitation, maybe even a mandate,"},{"time":714000,"text":"to enter the most vital arenas of human life,"},{"time":717000,"text":"the most sensitive and the most frightening,"},{"time":719000,"text":"the ones that we never want to go to,"},{"time":721000,"text":"but when we do go there,"},{"time":723000,"text":"we feel incredibly transformed when we do."},{"time":726000,"text":"And this also happened to my girls as they began to see,"},{"time":729000,"text":"and, we thought, maybe became an ounce more compassionate."},{"time":732000,"text":"One day, my daughter Tybee,"},{"time":734000,"text":"Tybee came to me, and she said, \"I have so much love for you in my body, daddy,"},{"time":737000,"text":"I can't stop giving you hugs and kisses."},{"time":739000,"text":"And when I have no more love left, I just drink milk,"},{"time":742000,"text":"because that's where love comes from.\""},{"time":744000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":746000,"text":"And one night my daughter Eden came to me."},{"time":748000,"text":"And as I lifted my leg out of bed,"},{"time":750000,"text":"she reached for my crutches and handed them to me."},{"time":753000,"text":"In fact, if I cling to one memory of this year,"},{"time":755000,"text":"it would be walking down a darkened hallway"},{"time":757000,"text":"with five spongy fingers"},{"time":759000,"text":"grasping the handle underneath my hand."},{"time":761000,"text":"I didn't need the crutch anymore,"},{"time":763000,"text":"I was walking on air."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766000,"text":"And one of the profound things that happened"},{"time":768000,"text":"was this act of actually connecting to all these people."},{"time":771000,"text":"And it made me think -- and I'll just note for the record --"},{"time":773000,"text":"one word that I've only heard once actually"},{"time":775000,"text":"was when we were all doing Tony Robbins yoga yesterday --"},{"time":778000,"text":"the one word that has not been mentioned in this seminar actually"},{"time":780000,"text":"is the word \"friend.\""},{"time":782000,"text":"And yet from everything we've been talking about --"},{"time":784000,"text":"compliance, or addiction, or weight loss --"},{"time":786000,"text":"we now know that community is important,"},{"time":788000,"text":"and yet it's one thing we don't actually bring in."},{"time":791000,"text":"And there was something incredibly profound"},{"time":793000,"text":"about sitting down with my closest friends"},{"time":795000,"text":"and telling them what they meant to me."},{"time":797000,"text":"And one of the things that I learned is that over time,"},{"time":799000,"text":"particularly men, who used to be non-communicative,"},{"time":802000,"text":"are becoming more and more communicative."},{"time":804000,"text":"And that particularly happened -- there was one in my life --"},{"time":806000,"text":"is this Council of Dads"},{"time":808000,"text":"that Linda said, what we were talking about,"},{"time":810000,"text":"it's like what the moms talk about at school drop-off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":813000,"text":"And no one captures this modern manhood to me"},{"time":815000,"text":"more than David Black."},{"time":817000,"text":"Now David is my literary agent."},{"time":819000,"text":"He's about five-foot three and a half on a good day,"},{"time":821000,"text":"standing fully upright in cowboy boots."},{"time":823000,"text":"And on kind of the manly-male front, he answers the phone --"},{"time":826000,"text":"I can say this I guess because you've done it here --"},{"time":828000,"text":"he answers the phone, \"Yo, motherfucker.\""},{"time":831000,"text":"He gives boring speeches about obscure bottles of wine,"},{"time":834000,"text":"and on his 50th birthday he bought a convertible sports car --"},{"time":837000,"text":"although, like a lot of men, he's impatient; he bought it on his 49th."},{"time":840000,"text":"But like a lot of modern men, he hugs, he bakes,"},{"time":843000,"text":"he leaves work early to coach Little League."},{"time":845000,"text":"Someone asked me if he cried when I asked him to be in the council of dads."},{"time":848000,"text":"I was like, \"David cries when you invite him to take a walk.\""},{"time":850000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":852000,"text":"But he's a literary agent,"},{"time":854000,"text":"which means he's a broker of dreams in a world where most dreams don't come true."},{"time":857000,"text":"And this is what we wanted him to capture --"},{"time":859000,"text":"what it means to have setbacks and then aspirations."},{"time":862000,"text":"And I said, \"What's the most valuable thing you can give to a dreamer?\""},{"time":865000,"text":"And he said, \"A belief in themselves.\""},{"time":868000,"text":"\"But when I came to see you,\" I said, \"I didn't believe in myself."},{"time":870000,"text":"I was at a wall.\""},{"time":872000,"text":"He said, \"I don't see the wall,\" and I'm telling you the same,"},{"time":874000,"text":"Don't see the wall."},{"time":876000,"text":"You may encounter one from time to time,"},{"time":878000,"text":"but you've got to find a way to get over it, around it, or through it."},{"time":880000,"text":"But whatever you do, don't succumb to it."},{"time":883000,"text":"Don't give in to the wall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":887000,"text":"My home is not far from the Brooklyn Bridge,"},{"time":890000,"text":"and during the year and a half I was on crutches,"},{"time":892000,"text":"it became a sort of symbol to me."},{"time":894000,"text":"So one day near the end of my journey,"},{"time":896000,"text":"I said, \"Come on girls, let's take a walk across the Brooklyn Bridge.\""},{"time":899000,"text":"We set out on crutches."},{"time":901000,"text":"I was on crutches, my wife was next to me,"},{"time":903000,"text":"my girls were doing these rockstar poses up ahead."},{"time":906000,"text":"And because walking was one of the first things I lost,"},{"time":909000,"text":"I spent most of that year"},{"time":911000,"text":"thinking about this most elemental of human acts."},{"time":913000,"text":"Walking upright, we are told,"},{"time":915000,"text":"is the threshold of what made us human."},{"time":918000,"text":"And yet, for the four million years humans have been walking upright,"},{"time":921000,"text":"the act is essentially unchanged."},{"time":923000,"text":"As my physical therapist likes to say,"},{"time":925000,"text":"\"Every step is a tragedy waiting to happen.\""},{"time":928000,"text":"You nearly fall with one leg,"},{"time":930000,"text":"then you catch yourself with the other."},{"time":933000,"text":"And the biggest consequence of walking on crutches --"},{"time":935000,"text":"as I did for a year and a half --"},{"time":937000,"text":"is that you walk slower."},{"time":939000,"text":"You hurry,"},{"time":941000,"text":"you get where you're going, but you get there alone."},{"time":944000,"text":"You go slow, you get where you're going,"},{"time":946000,"text":"but you get there with this community"},{"time":948000,"text":"you built along the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"At the risk of admission, I was never nicer"},{"time":952000,"text":"than the year I was on crutches."},{"time":954000,"text":"200 years ago,"},{"time":956000,"text":"a new type of pedestrian appeared in Paris."},{"time":959000,"text":"He was called a \"flaneur,\" one who wanders the arcades."},{"time":962000,"text":"And it was the custom of those flaneurs"},{"time":965000,"text":"to show they were men of leisure"},{"time":967000,"text":"by taking turtles for walks"},{"time":969000,"text":"and letting the reptile set the pace."},{"time":972000,"text":"And I just love this ode to slow moving."},{"time":974000,"text":"And it's become my own motto for my girls."},{"time":977000,"text":"Take a walk with a turtle."},{"time":979000,"text":"Behold the world in pause."},{"time":982000,"text":"And this idea of pausing"},{"time":984000,"text":"may be the single biggest lesson I took from my journey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":987000,"text":"There's a quote from Moses"},{"time":989000,"text":"on the side of the Liberty Bell,"},{"time":991000,"text":"and it comes from a passage in the book of Leviticus,"},{"time":994000,"text":"that every seven years you should let the land lay fallow."},{"time":997000,"text":"And every seven sets of seven years,"},{"time":999000,"text":"the land gets an extra year of rest"},{"time":1002000,"text":"during which time all families are reunited"},{"time":1004000,"text":"and people surrounded with the ones they love."},{"time":1007000,"text":"That 50th year is called the jubilee year,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"and it's the origin of that term."},{"time":1012000,"text":"And though I'm shy of 50,"},{"time":1014000,"text":"it captures my own experience."},{"time":1016000,"text":"My lost year was my jubilee year."},{"time":1019000,"text":"By laying fallow,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"I planted the seeds for a healthier future"},{"time":1023000,"text":"and was reunited with the ones I love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1026000,"text":"Come the one year anniversary of my journey,"},{"time":1028000,"text":"I went to see my surgeon, Dr. John Healey --"},{"time":1030000,"text":"and by the way, Healey, great name for a doctor."},{"time":1034000,"text":"He's the president of the International Society of Limb Salvage,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"which is the least euphemistic term I've ever heard."},{"time":1040000,"text":"And I said, \"Dr. Healey, if my daughters come to you one day"},{"time":1043000,"text":"and say, 'What should I learn from my daddy's story?'"},{"time":1045000,"text":"what would you tell them?\""},{"time":1047000,"text":"He said, \"I would tell them what I know,"},{"time":1049000,"text":"and that is everybody dies,"},{"time":1053000,"text":"but not everybody lives."},{"time":1056000,"text":"I want you to live.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1058000,"text":"I wrote a letter to my girls"},{"time":1060000,"text":"that appears at the end of my book, \"The Council of Dads,\""},{"time":1062000,"text":"and I listed these lessons,"},{"time":1064000,"text":"a few of which you've heard here today:"},{"time":1066000,"text":"Approach the cow, pack your flipflops,"},{"time":1068000,"text":"don't see the wall,"},{"time":1070000,"text":"live the questions,"},{"time":1072000,"text":"harvest miracles."},{"time":1074000,"text":"As I looked at this list -- to me it was sort of like a psalm book of living --"},{"time":1077000,"text":"I realized, we may have done it for our girls,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"but it really changed us."},{"time":1082000,"text":"And that is, the secret of the Council of Dads,"},{"time":1084000,"text":"is that my wife and I did this"},{"time":1086000,"text":"in an attempt to help our daughters,"},{"time":1089000,"text":"but it really changed us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1091000,"text":"So I stand here today"},{"time":1093000,"text":"as you see now, walking without crutches or a cane."},{"time":1097000,"text":"And last week I had my 18-month scans."},{"time":1099000,"text":"And as you all know,"},{"time":1101000,"text":"anybody with cancer has to get follow-up scans."},{"time":1103000,"text":"In my case it's quarterly."},{"time":1105000,"text":"And all the collective minds in this room, I dare say,"},{"time":1107000,"text":"can never find a solution for scan-xiety."},{"time":1110000,"text":"As I was going there, I was wondering, what would I say"},{"time":1112000,"text":"depending on what happened here."},{"time":1116000,"text":"I got good news that day,"},{"time":1118000,"text":"and I stand here today cancer-free,"},{"time":1120000,"text":"walking without aid"},{"time":1122000,"text":"and hobbling forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1125000,"text":"And I just want to mention briefly in passing -- I'm past my time limit --"},{"time":1128000,"text":"but I just want to briefly mention in passing"},{"time":1130000,"text":"that one of the nice things that can come out of a conference like this"},{"time":1132000,"text":"is, at a similar meeting,"},{"time":1134000,"text":"back in the spring,"},{"time":1136000,"text":"Anne Wojcicki heard about our story"},{"time":1138000,"text":"and very quickly -- in a span of three weeks --"},{"time":1140000,"text":"put the full resources of 23andMe,"},{"time":1142000,"text":"and we announced an initiative in July"},{"time":1145000,"text":"to get to decode the genome"},{"time":1147000,"text":"of anybody, a living person"},{"time":1150000,"text":"with a heart tissue, bone sarcoma."},{"time":1153000,"text":"And she told me last night, in the three months since we've done it,"},{"time":1156000,"text":"we've gotten 300 people who've contributed to this program."},{"time":1159000,"text":"And the epidemiologists here will tell you,"},{"time":1161000,"text":"that's half the number of people who get the disease"},{"time":1163000,"text":"in one year in the United States."},{"time":1165000,"text":"So if you go to 23andMe,"},{"time":1167000,"text":"or if you go to councilofdads.com, you can click on a link."},{"time":1170000,"text":"And we encourage anybody to join this effort."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1173000,"text":"But I'll just close what I've been talking about"},{"time":1176000,"text":"by leaving you with this message:"},{"time":1178000,"text":"May you find an excuse to reach out to some long-lost pal,"},{"time":1180000,"text":"or to that college roommate,"},{"time":1182000,"text":"or to some person you may have turned away from."},{"time":1184000,"text":"May you find a mud puddle to jump in someplace,"},{"time":1187000,"text":"or find a way to get over, around, or through any wall"},{"time":1189000,"text":"that stands between you and one of your dreams."},{"time":1192000,"text":"And every now and then,"},{"time":1194000,"text":"find a friend, find a turtle,"},{"time":1196000,"text":"and take a long, slow walk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1199000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1202000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}